0至60克脂肪、2400毫克鈉，可見18件雞的卡路里及鈉已佔成年人可攝取量一大半，脂肪更已經超標，加上尚未計算伴隨麥樂雞的醬料，不建議市民大量食用。<br />\n<br />\n另外，如果正餐只吃麥樂雞，欠缺蔬果、澱粉質等營養元素，他呼籲市民特別注意，「雖然睇落好似冇乜嘢，但其實問題好大」。</blockquote><br />\n屌，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩撚完"},{"pid":"033aeca31af53f410aeb86a5e94c8e35acb3334a","tid":450452,"uid":61331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"每次食完D屎都臭到仆街 但係又好撚想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc10a16309abac1d36644a9d0b7891be41d6104","tid":450452,"uid":72173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"麥當勞自己hold起個獎品啦<br />\n<br />\n去食佢個餐咁撚傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fd228d6b7967bed9189db87e18d46a35775b2d","tid":450452,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:41:06.000Z","msg":"仲未牙肉痛生痱滋？"},{"pid":"88d5c45f6103a8fe110c091ba2654ba1184d5b33","tid":450452,"uid":33719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"樓主係個D成面暗瘡既死毒撚"},{"pid":"f2aa8233a0789d4c024bfb5b9ffe559208d9f0ae","tid":450452,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係個D成面暗瘡既死毒撚</blockquote><br />\n類似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2c1610b039a73896ead26e586bdcd508e105da","tid":450452,"uid":20544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T17:18:05.000Z","msg":"我食佐2次<br />\n應該唔會再食<br />\n未試過食m記真係覺得飽"},{"pid":"e6c208ff61df22b4bae9ec4eeebd1c8f2ad2f3a6","tid":450452,"uid":37226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T18:13:19.000Z","msg":"我都想食 但佢唔撚比人4個都揀蜜糖芥末醬"},{"pid":"0987918dab9dbbfa70c4fef7035115a690a9e176","tid":450452,"uid":12754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" cl